# Excel to JSON Converter

This project is a small web app that converts Excel and CSV files into JSON with a modern interface, editable preview, and export tools.

## Features

- Drag and drop upload area
- Excel and CSV support
- Multiple sheets support
- JSON preview with syntax highlight
- JSON download
- JSON to Excel conversion
- Dark and light theme toggle

## Open the App

1. Open the project folder.
2. Double-click [Index.html](./Index.html) or open it in your browser.
3. Upload an `.xlsx`, `.xls`, or `.csv` file to start converting.

## Project Files

- `Index.html` - app structure
- `styles.css` - app styles
- `app.js` - app logic
